<h3>Prioritize Technical Gaps Correctly</h3>
<p>If a competitor passes Core Web Vitals and your site fails, that technical gap affects every page. Not just one keyword. Technical deficiencies suppress organic growth at the category level.</p>
<p>Prioritize technical fixes above content creation when your scores are significantly below competitors. A faster, cleaner site multiplies the ranking impact of every piece of new content.</p>
